sentences.en: Jane moved aimlessly down the tree-lined street, not knowing where she was heading.
sentences.cn: 简漫无目的地沿着绿树成荫的街道走着，不知道该去往何方。

sentences.en: They are really pretty little towns with lots of old houses and beautiful tree-lined streets.
sentences.cn: 它们是真的是非常漂亮的小镇，有很多老房子和美丽的绿树成荫的街道。

sentences.en: London is blessed with plenty of parks and tree-lined streets.
sentences.cn: 伦敦有许多的公园和绿树成荫的街道。
